    "1. Why are functions advantageous to have in your programs?\n",
    "Answer:\n",
    "\n",
    "Functions are advantageous to have in your programs as it helps in code reusabliy and with the help of *args and **args it helps to optimize the parameter field as well.\n",
    "\n",
    "Functions help in DRY concept(Do Not Repeat Yourself)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "1d39aa74",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "2. When does the code in a function run: when it's specified or when it's called?\n",
    "Answer : \n",
    "\n",
    "A code in a function runs when it is called,Once the function is called it goes to the block where the function is defined."
   ]
  },
